    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p><code>FileUtils.readFileToString</code> doesn't work with <code>StandardCharsets.UTF_8</code>.</p>\n\n<p>Instead, try</p>\n\n<p><code>FileUtils.readFileToString(customersFile, \"UTF-8\");</code></p>\n\n<p>or</p>\n\n<p><code>FileUtils.readFileToString(customersFile, StandardCharsets.UTF_8.name());</code></p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 3527008,
      "reputation" : 2115,
      "user_id" : 2947812,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 63,
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/Ia1v7.jpg?s=256",
      "display_name" : "Mikhail Batcer",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/2947812/mikhail-batcer"
