  "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/questions/28478765/fileutils-readfiletostring-from-apache-commons-io-works-incorrectly-with-cyril",
  "title" : "FileUtils.readFileToString() from Apache Commons IO works incorrectly with Cyrillic",
  "body" : "<p>I am using FileUtils.readFileToString to read contents of a text file with JSON at once. The file is UTF-8 encoded (w/o BOM). Yet, instead of cyrillic letters I get ?????? signs. Why?</p>\n\n<pre><code>public String getJSON() throws IOException\n{\n    File customersFile = new File(this.STORAGE_FILE_PATH);\n    return FileUtils.readFileToString(customersFile, StandardCharsets.UTF_8);\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
}